properties.name: plot
properties.sample: Story of the lives of three Soviet pilots who are united by disaster in a small town in the mountains.

properties.name: fullplot
properties.sample: This movie is about a crew of a passenger plane and consists of two parts. The first part tells about personal lives of the characters, their successes and failures, relationships inside their families and between each others. The second part has them land the plane in the airport of a city called Bidri, which was damaged by an earthquake. They try to fly people to safety, but just as they land, another earthquake hits, and now the chances of a successful takeoff are slim...

properties.name: consensus
properties.sample: This remake of Planet of the Apes can't compare to the original in some critics' mind, but the striking visuals and B-movie charms may win you over.
